    <h1>Highpoint "unlock you style"</h1>

    <p>
      To bring Highpoint’s AW15 trends to life we launched Unlock Your Style, an innovative and fully integrated campaign that ran for two weeks. We developed a mobile first experience where customers could create their own style combinations using a carefully curated range of products from Highpoint’s leading retailers. Shoppers could scroll through hundreds of tops, bottoms, jackets and accessories, before settling on their perfect combination from the 100,000,000 available.
    </p>

    <p>
      To really bring the campaign to life, we constructed a 3m x 1.8m screen in centre, which was used to display the individual flat lays being curated in real time by customers, as well as the trending products based on popularity. The screen served as a constant reminder of the campaign for shoppers that were in centre, helping extend its reach and impact. Through the data we collected, we were also able to gain valuable insights into which items, trends and combinations the shoppers were loving.
    </p>

    <p>
      To encourage users to get involved, a Highpoint gift card was given away every hour that the competition was running. Just for entering, customers could also receive discounts from their favourite Highpoint retailers.
    </p>
