    <h2>Choose your style</h2>

    <p>
      Through a responsive website users could select a combination from 5 different types of clothing, from top to bottom. When all 5 were selected users were shown a result, where their 'flatlay' would be matched with a current trend based on what items they picked. 
    </p>
    <p>
      Once submitted the user would get the possible message that they've won a prize but also that their 'flatlay' was send to a queue to be displayed on the big screen in the shopping mall. We created a small API where the big screen would continuesly ping the API for new flatlays to add to the queue. If the queue would be empty it would get a set of old entries.
    </p>
  </section>

