    <h2>Animating on a 4k resolution</h2>
    <p>
      We knew our biggest challenge in this case would be running animations on a "web page" on a 4k resolution screen. Sure, there a better ways to solve this, but with learnings from earlier projects we knew this was possible. In total 8 different animations were developed that matched every fashion trend for that year. 
    </p>
    <p>
      All animations were tested multiple times and finetuned where needed. The majority of the animations were built upon the <a href="http://velocityjs.org/">velocity.js framework</a>, but in 2 cases a simple CSS animation was chosen.
    </p>

    <p>
      After showing 10 entries the screen would show the most popular clothing items per trend.
    </p>

