    <h2>The results</h2>
    <p>
      Unlock Your Style was a huge success amassing over 25,000 entries in the two week period and smashing our target by over 150%. On just day two of the campaign entries were already coming already in fast, with over 3,500 entries over the course of the day. Our activity on Facebook and other platforms helped sustain momentum and kept entries consistent throughout the duration of the competition. Users spent on average of almost 10 minutes engaging with the different options within the app.
